snippet.title: Tarnished Keeper is Here - The Binding of Isaac Epiphany Mod
snippet.description:
Tarnished Keeper has arrived.

The Binding of Isaac Epiphany is a mod that adds "Tarnished" Characters, or Super Tainted Characters to Isaac. Multiple Tarnished Characters are playable now. 

Join the discord server: https://discord.gg/PYkKRMjbpm 
Join my discord server: https://discord.gg/HBTyPM8

Steam workshop Page: https://steamcommunity.com/sharedfile...
